" strong="H7043">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H5600">navire</char>. Mais <char style="w" strong="H3124">Jonas</char> <char style="w" strong="H3220">était</char> <char style="w" strong="H3381">descendu</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">dans</char> <char style="w" strong="H3220">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H3411">profondeurs</char> <char style="w" strong="H3381">du</char> <char style="w" strong="H5600">navire</char>, il <char style="w" strong="H3220">était</char> <char style="w" strong="H7901">couché</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H7901">dormait</char> <char style="w" strong="H7290">profondément</char>. <verse eid="JON 1:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JON 1:6" />Alors <char style="w" strong="H7121">le</char> capitaine <char style="w" strong="H7121">du</char> navire s'approcha <char style="w" strong="H7227">de</char> lui <char style="w" strong="H6965">et</char> lui dit : « <char style="w" strong="H7227">Que</char> veux-tu <char style="w" strong="H7121">dire</char>, dormeur ? Lève-toi, <char style="w" strong="H7121">invoque</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">ton</char> Dieu !<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ou, dieux</char></note> Peut-être <char style="w" strong="H7121">ton</char> Dieu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ou, dieux </char></note> nous remarquera-t-il, afin <char style="w" strong="H7227">que</char> nous <char style="w" strong="H3808">ne</char> périssions <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char>. »<verse eid="JON 1:6" /></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JON 1:7" />
    <char style="w" strong="H3212">Ils</char> <char style="w" strong="H3212">se</char> dirent <char style="w" strong="H3212">tous</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">les</char> uns <char style="w" strong="H7451">aux</char> <char style="w" strong="H7453">autres</char> : « <char style="w" strong="H3212">Venez</char> ! <char style="w" strong="H5307">Tirons</char> <char style="w" strong="H5307">au</char> <char style="w" strong="H1486">sort</char>, afin <char style="w" strong="H5921">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">savoir</char> <char style="w" strong="H4310">qui</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">est</char> responsable <char style="w" strong="H5921">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5307">ce</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">mal</char> <char style="w" strong="H4310">qui</char> <char style="w" strong="H3212">nous</char> frappe. » <char style="w" strong="H3212">Ils</char> <char style="w" strong="H5307">tirèrent</char> donc <char style="w" strong="H5307">au</char> <char style="w" strong="H1486">sort</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3212">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3045">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H1486">sort</char> <char style="w" strong="H5307">tomba</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H3124">Jonas</char>. <verse eid="JON 1:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JON 1:8" /><char style="w" strong="H5971">Ils</char> <char style="w" strong="H5971">lui</char> demandèrent alors : « Dis-nous, je t'en <char style="w" strong="H4994">prie</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5046">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H2063">cause</char> <char style="w" strong="H5971">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5971">qui</char> <char style="w" strong="H2088">ce</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">malheur</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">est</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">sur</char> nous. <char style="w" strong="H4100">Quelle</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">est</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">ta</char> profession ? D'où viens-tu ? <char style="w" strong="H4100">Quel</char> <char style="w" strong="H7451">est</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">ton</char> pays ? <char style="w" strong="H5971">De</char> <char style="w" strong="H4100">quel</char> <char style="w" strong="H5971">peuple</char> es-tu ? »<verse eid="JON 1:8" /></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JON 1:9" />
    <char style="w" strong="H3068">Il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">leur</char> dit : « Je suis <char style="w" strong="H5680">hébreu</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> je <char style="w" strong="H3373">crains</char> Yahvé, <char style="w" strong="H6213">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">Dieu</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Le mot hébreu rendu par « Dieu » est « אֱלֹהִ֑ים » (Elohim).</char></note> <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> <char style="w" strong="H8064">cieux</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">a</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">fait</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H3220">mer</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H6213">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H3004">terre</char> <char style="w" strong="H3004">sèche</char>. »<verse eid="JON 1:9" /></para>
  <para style="p">
